column5: Awesome fish Mike. Congrats !
What a tank!  Nicely done man!
haha...  makes you wonder how she made it to that size...  still cant believe after a lengthy battle and losing the fish... it hit the same bait again...  ...
Wow that is a real decent fish. There is even bigger ones in that area. Congrats
Awesome fish, congrats!
I didn't say where it came from...
very sweet Mike. Just an amazing fish. Congrats on the PB
Congrats Mike. What a hog!!
That IS a goody!!!  WTG dood!

Well the girlfriend got off early today... So I got to go fishing tonight...  Well me and a buddy fished for about an hour before we marked our first fish.. Wich refused our offerings... And so did the next 5 marks... We tried everything...  Again... I decided to use my go to lure... And work on the cadence...  Finally get I bite... Swing and a miss... Got my minnow...  Rebaited and dropped... Bang got him that time... A nice 18-20 incher...  Soon after my partner got SMOKED on his lindy darter... I guess they do work...lol  I get cracked again... Feels huge... I'd gain 3-4 feet and she would take it right back... Work her up 20 feet and POP... Hook pulled....  I was devastated....  As I rebait I watched the beast swim back down... I dropped my bait back down... And before the fish made it to the bottom it saw my lure again... That's right... It hit again!!!!! After I just lost it seconds before...  This time I got it up to the hole... OMG... Beast... I wasn't sure if it would fit through the 6 inch hole...  We got her through the hole barely...  She went 31x18 wich is 12lbs on the calculator... My new PB  We later iced 2 more 18-20 inchers...  What a great night
What a freakin beast man !!!!! Nice going  She looks like she's been eating well. Congrats on the PB
Nice Mike!  Cheers, Ron...
Nice fish Mike. That thing is a beast.
Massive walleye! If you don't mind saying, what do u mean by cadence?
How dare you MM! You can't afford that fish!  Amazing catch, what a beauty!!!!
